snippet.title: Kanpeki - Demo Release
snippet.description:
Dragged into her own mind, Hoshi, a fashion obsessed high-schooler must escape a twisted version of her rural hometown. A survival horror game about perfectionism.

Check it out here : https://wiloux.itch.io/kanpeki

Twitter : https://twitter.com/streetlightteam
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/streetlightstudio_/
